# Commands

## Initialize project
``` terraform init ```

## Validate sintax
``` terraform validate ```

## View plan	 
``` terraform plan ```

## Deploy
``` terraform apply ```

## Delete deploy
``` terraform destroy ```

## View Deployment
``` terraform show ```

## View state
```terraform state list```

## Remove resource from state
```terraform state rm [state path]


